task.summary: Added CMakeLists.txt to compile with CLion. Changed call convention of dll to __stdcall. Added more tests to test_jmlaser_api.cpp
Added initial draft of C++ API.
C++ API for jmlaser.dll finished. Added test app for C++ API.

Improved robustness of jmlaser C++ API against invalid parameters.
Added accessors for jmlaser C++ API fields. Added setter for projector friendly name. Improved efficiency of jmlaser C++ API (object parameters passed by reference).

Improved robustness of jmlaser C++ API against invalid parameters.
Added accessors for jmlaser C++ API fields. Added setter for projector friendly name. Improved efficiency of jmlaser C++ API (object parameters passed by reference).
Added safety resize of number of points in output frame acording to projector limits.
Changed JMVectorStruct to ensure C compatability (C++ POD Struct).
Updated jmlaser.h according to IDA Pro disassembler analysis.

Added retrieval of step, min and max projection speed and also the projector ip address.
Added square, plus and cross test patterns.
Improved robustness against static calls without prior device enumeration.
